Introduction

Kang Yunjeong, also known as Gemma Kang, is a South Korean singer under Prain Global.

She was a contestant on the mystery music game shows I Can See Your Voice 8 in 2021 and Art Singer in 2022.

She was also a contestant on the JTBC survival show Girls On Fire where she ended up ranking #4 which made her a part of the final group on June 25, 2024.

However, on December 23, 2024, it was announced that the debut of the final group had been canceled.
